  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Offset rationale documents why acceptance is justified despite this shortfall. This is a fully-clean negative-control package; no weakener should fire.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-noncannulated-compression-bending",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-qoi-within-10pct",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-ensemble-noncannulated",
